<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn359">  359  It is possible that the four watchers are actually in the children's rooms and peering into their beds; this would explain the striking sense of immediacy of vision. The Four fear, then, not alone that their whispers but also that their footfalls may wake the sleepers.  </div>
